__ Cantrip: Groan ____________________________ Cost: 15 ______________________

Use:  cantrip groan                            Material Component: none
Use:  C groan

The cantrip groan is a minor magic of the sphere of illusion.  Once cast,
the sounds of groaning will be heard in the immediate area for a few minutes.
A useless, and mostly tasteless cantrip.  To dispel the cantrip, say
< groan off >
